name: TrainBox
body:
### Welcome to X!
This heading would contain the name of our project, but we still need more people to visit https://github.com/thomasahle/TrinityProject/wiki/TheyCallMeStacey and vote on a name.

The background story of the game is going to be something about delivering stuff with trains in space, but the trains have arrived in a bad order. (Like udp packages?)

### Try our game!
Try out [our latest build directly from your browser](http://thomasahle.github.com/TrinityProject/game/TrainBox.html)! If the level of playability is not yet high enough to satisfy you, we crafted [some demo levels](https://github.com/thomasahle/TrinityProject/wiki/Levels-and-algebra) for you to test how smart you are.

### Authors and Contributors
- Edward Shaw (@EdShaw)
- Matthew Pellegrini (@MattPellegrini)
- Elena Sizikova (@esizikova)
- Colin Bian (@colinbian)
- Thomas Ahle (@thomasahle)

### Support or Contact
You can't do this.
